{
  "texts": [
    "This human-AI decision making setup defers a fraction of all instances to experts.",
    "We investigate explanation usefulness for finetuning/prompting LLMs to defer, and to human decision makers.",
    "We finetune Llama-2-13B-Chat and gpt-3.5--turbo-1106, and prompt gpt-4o-2024-05-13.",
    "We use 1.4K model's dev-set predictions for finetuning, 371 predictions for testing deferral models,",
    "13 A two-proportion z-test yields p-value of 0.03 for P3."
  ]
}